title: "Beyond Taming Technical Debt" with Marijn Huizendveld

media:group.media:title: "Beyond Taming Technical Debt" with Marijn Huizendveld
media:group.media:description:
Skills Matter Online Meetups are a virtual meetup on the topics that truly matter to today's developers.

Join us weekdays at 5:00 pm GMT (UK local time) when we'll be joined by an expert from around the globe for a 40 minute talk followed by a Q&A session.

Each session will explore topics such as functional languages, mobile development, agile methodologies and machine learning.

Learn more at skillsmatter.com/thursdays
